Springfield Armory® answered that question in 2007 with the introduction of the Enhanced Micro Pistol™. The shorter dimensions also work to increase reliability – something that’s crucial in a concealed carry pistol. And of course, the overall dimensions are one of the smallest 1911s out there.The good news doesn’t stop with the innovative design.
